title: Subatomic Sound System - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Subatomic Sound System performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded April 22, 2023

Songs:
Champion Sound
Chase The Devil
Lee "Scratch" Perry Is The Dub Organizer
Babylon Soon Fall

Emch -  Dub Mixing & Melodica
Screechy Dan - Vocals
Troy Shaka Simms - Saxophone
Larry McDonald - Percussion

Lee “Scratch” Perry’s vocals featured on “Chase the Devil” and “Lee "Scratch" Perry Is The Dub Organizer”

Host: Kid Hops
Audio Engineers: Kevin Suggs, Jon Roberts
Audio Mixer: Emch
Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro, Scott Holpainen
Editor: Scott Holpainen
